headline: The Price of a Standoff: Disney’s Losses (Or Wins) from the YouTube TV Blackout
summary: According to Morgan Stanley’s analysts, Disney could be losing approximately $30 million per week during the YouTube TV blackout if the latter lasts for 14days.
